flowRoot.flowPara: Has a customized rpm package for each web application used in the web environment.
Let administrators to decide which application to have on their specific web environment.
Example of packages in this repo are: apache, mailman, moin, trac, mantis, phpbb, drupal, wordpress, ...
Is used as main development ground. All web applications that need to be customized will have a branch here.
Here is the base source code used by rpm packagers.
Here is where developers work to give each web application a common design and gear one another.
